channel.title: Need lot's of help coding on my 508. (will update frequently)
channel.description:
[ul][left]Alright Guys thanks for stopping in and even thinking about helping me :) So a couple of friends and I are opening a new server and I need alot of help but I will post certain things every now and again of stuff that I could not find. [list] [li]First: Donator symbol for donators. (also if you dont mind I need help creating a command to give it ingame. which can be done by someone with the player rights of 1 or higher.[/li] [li]Second: I need help with my mute commands and etc so it can be used by mods not just admins.[/li][/list] My ::givemod / giveadmin commands are also not working along with demoting someone My ::jail is also broken :/
Sorry guys im a new coder and just wanna learn :/ if it matters im on the Mezzyscape508 server[/ul]
[/left]
